      "author": "scottTomaszewski",
      "description": "## New Features:\r\n\r\n- Added support for multiple Inline Admonition \"Types.\"  A Type is the way an Inline Admonition is triggered, such as with a prefix or suffix\r\n- Added \"Suffix\" Type: an Inline Admonition triggered by text at the end of a codeblock\r\n- Added \"Contains\" Type: an Inline Admonition triggered by text anywhere in a codeblock\r\n\r\n## Other Notes\r\n\r\n- The formatting of plugin setting data was overhauled.  There should be a migration of the data to the new format.",
